  Kinetic (Delta T^0):                   1.271998224532561         34.6128           798.19          3339.63
  Delta V^Pauli Coulomb:                -0.773824040858865        -21.0568          -485.58         -2031.67
  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.278501980116219         -7.5784          -174.76          -731.21
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.074004705615366          2.0138            46.44           194.30
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.041600628001367         -1.1320           -26.10          -109.22
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.252076281171474          6.8593           158.18           661.83
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

